To run the tests:

1) Setup the environment and make sure you have created the libvgrid.a
in src:
. setup_{arch+compiler}.dot
make clean
make genlib

2) cd test_lib; make clean

3) Compile and run all the tests 
./testlibvgrid.sh

All tests must Succeeded

All tests done in WORK
All stdout in *.out
data input in data
data output in data_out
Source test code: *.F90 or *.c

4) If one or more test fails, rerun it one by one to debug it
cd WORK
vi write_stat.F90
make write_stat
write_stat 

5) Run the tests on all supported platforms and for all compilers.
